  <div class="row align-items-center">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>Let Eventerate Handle the Details</h3>
      <p class="text-muted">Save time with smart automation. Eventerate takes care of logistics, schedules, and planning so you can focus on what truly matters.</p>
